Homepage: http://ros.org/wiki/hrpsys
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-hydro-hrpsys
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, freeglut3-dev, libirrlicht-dev, libqhull-dev, libsdl1.2-dev, libxml2-dev, libxmu-dev, ros-hydro-opencv2, ros-hydro-openhrp3
Description: Basic RT components and utilities to control robots using OpenRTM. This package is a wrapper of its upstream repository. Its development is happening at code.google.com/p/hrpsys-base. The upstream version number to date is 3.1.4. Please refer to this discussion (http://code.google.com/p/rtm-ros-robotics/issues/detail?id=159) for the reason of this version conversion.
